                        <p><strong>Spam Lunging Strike</strong> — Dash from target to target. Lunging Strike is your only active damage skill. Hold the button and let the auto-targeting do the work.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Walking Arsenal</strong> — Maintained automatically through Barbarian weapon swaps during Lunging Strike. Provides all three weapon mastery bonuses at once.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Repeat Shouts</strong> — When buffs expire, cycle through War Cry, Challenging Shout, and Iron Skin again. With CDR, they should be back up quickly.</p>
