                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Never let Fury hit zero.</strong>
                    <p>Hooves of the Mountain God drains your Fury for the wide cleaves. When Fury reaches zero, you lose the AoE and become squishy (no Fury = no Melted Heart DR). Keep shouts up for Fury gen.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Walking Arsenal is free damage.</strong>
                    <p>The Barbarian's weapon swap mechanic activates Walking Arsenal passively. You don't need to do anything special — Lunging Strike naturally cycles your weapons.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
